# Title: Service Started/Stopped Via Wmic.EXE
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-06-20
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects usage of wmic to start or stop a service
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.t1047
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_wmic_service_manipulation.yml

CommandLine IN ("*stopservice*", "*startservice*") CommandLine="* service *" CommandLine="* call *" OriginalFileName="wmic.exe" OR Image="*\\WMIC.exe"